===Alternative forms===
* {{alt|pt|axadrez}}
===Etymology===
From {{inh|pt|roa-opt|axadrez}}, {{m|roa-opt|enxadrez}}, from {{der|pt|xaa|شطرنج|الشَطْرَنْج|tr=aš-šaṭranj}}, from {{der|pt|ar|شَطْرَنْج|t=chess}}, from {{der|pt|fa|شترنگ|tr=šatrang}}, from {{der|pt|pal|𐭰𐭠𐭲𐭫𐭠𐭭𐭢|tr=ctlng|ts=čatrang|t=chess}}, from {{der|pt|sa|चतुरङ्ग|tr=cátur-aṅga|lit=four parts}} {{q|of an army: king, elephants, horses, foot soldiers}}.
Cognate with {{cog|gl|xadrez}}, {{cog|ast|axedrez}}, {{cog|mwl|xadreç}}, {{cog|es|ajedrez}} and {{cog|an|axedrez}}.
